# Integration & Polish Plan

## Goal
Consolidate the app into a single polished Streamlit application with CSS styling, auto-thresholds, and cleanup.

## Proposed Changes

### 1. Auto-Threshold (No Slider)
- **Piano Mode**: `velocity_threshold = 0.5`
- **Drums Mode**: `velocity_threshold = 0.15`
- Remove sidebar slider, set automatically based on mode.

### 2. CSS/HTML Styling
- Dark theme with neon accents
- Custom title styling
- Status indicators with color

### 3. Console Logs
- Add `[AUDIO]`, `[DETECT]`, `[HIT]` prefixes
- Timestamp each log

### 4. File Cleanup
- **Keep**: [ar_studio.py](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/PycharmProjects/AirPlay/ar_studio.py), [hand_landmarker.task](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/PycharmProjects/AirPlay/hand_landmarker.task), [sounds/](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/PycharmProjects/AirPlay/ar_studio.py#78-125), `drum_sounds/`, `keyboard_one_octave (1).jpg`
- **Delete**: [app.py](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/PycharmProjects/AirPlay/app.py) (deprecated), [hand_landmarker.ipynb](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/PycharmProjects/AirPlay/hand_landmarker.ipynb), [piano_keys.png](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/PycharmProjects/AirPlay/piano_keys.png)

### 5. Final File Structure
```
AirPlay/
├── ar_studio.py          # Main unified app
├── hand_landmarker.task  # MediaPipe model
├── sounds/               # Piano sounds
├── drum_sounds/          # Drum sounds
